{"name":"Greater Water Elemental","size":"huge","type":"Elemental","tag":"","alignment":"neutral","hitDice":"23","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"14 (natural armor)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"90","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"157 (15d12 + 60)","speedDesc":"30 ft., swim 90 ft.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"20","conPoints":"19","intPoints":"5","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"8","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"12","customCr":"5 (1,800 XP)","customProf":3,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The water elemental can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The water elemental regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the water elemental can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the water elemental can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The water elemental can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the water elemental's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the water elemental's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the water elemental dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Water Form","desc":"The [MON] can enter a hostile creature's space and stop there. It can move through a space as narrow as 1 inch wide without squeezing. Additionally, the [MON] can have up to 3 large creatures grappled inside of it at a time."},{"name":"Riptide","desc":"The first time the [MON] enters a creature's space on its turn, that creature must make a DC [STR SAVE] strength saving throw, or be knocked prone."},{"name":"Freeze","desc":"If the [MON] takes 10 or more cold damage in a turn, it partially freezes; its speed is reduced by 20 feet and it loses its resistance to nonmagical bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage until the end of its next turn."},{"name":"Reactive","desc":"The [MON] can take three reactions on every round in combat."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes three slam attacks, one of which it may replace with a use of its Whelm."},{"name":"Slam","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 3d8] bludgeoning damage. If this attack targets a creature restrained in the [MON]'s space, the creature must succeed on a DC [CON SAVE] constitution saving throw or lose its held breath and begin to suffocate."},{"name":"Whelm","desc":"Each creature in the [MON]'s space must make a DC [STR SAVE] Strength saving throw. On a failure, a target takes [3d8] bludgeoning damage. If it is Large or smaller, it is also grappled (escape DC 15). Until this grapple ends, the target is restrained and unable to breathe unless it can breathe water. If the saving throw is successful, the target is pushed out of the elemental's space.\nAt the start of each of the [MON]'s turns, each target grappled by it takes [3d8] bludgeoning damage. A creature within 5 feet of the [MON] can pull a creature or object out of it by taking an action to make a DC [STR SAVE] Strength and succeeding."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[{"name":"Crashing Wave","desc":"When the [MON] is missed with a melee attack, it can move up to 5 feet toward the attacker and use it's Whelm."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"dex","order":1},{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"acid","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"fire","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"poison","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"exhaustion"},{"name":"grappled"},{"name":"paralyzed"},{"name":"petrified"},{"name":"poisoned"},{"name":"prone"},{"name":"restrained"},{"name":"unconscious"}],"languages":[{"name":"Aquan","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}